data.description: Nestled in the heart of Western Branch, this updated 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom brick home exudes charm and versatility. As you enter, the spacious living areas greet you with an open invitation to host guests and create lasting memories.  Upstairs, the primary bedroom serves as a tranquil retreat, boasting a generous walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite bathroom featuring a jetted soaking tub and walk-in shower. Throughout most of the house, hardwood floors lend an elegant touch, seamlessly connecting the updated kitchen, equipped with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances, to the cozy fireplace and the expansive back deck for both indoor and outdoor enjoyment. This captivating property combines modern comforts with timeless appeal, and it's an opportunity you won't want to miss.
